## Configuracion del mod rewrite para URL amigables RewriteEngine On RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} ^/system.* RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php?/$1 [L] RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d RewriteRule ^(.+)$ index.php?/$1 [L] ErrorDocument 404 index.php - See more at: http://www.diegodicamillo.com.ar/blog/2012/09/19/no-input-file-specified-codeigniter-error-problema-resuelto/#sthash.OrJ1xyJL.dpuf